                    <lb/><supplied reason="lost">מ</supplied>שנברה העול<supplied reason="lost"
                        >ם</supplied><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>
                    <lb/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>לי בו יהי של<supplied
                        reason="lost">ום</supplied><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>
                    <lb/>
                    <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/></p>
